sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant R as Ride Service
    participant D as Driver Service
    participant X as Redis Offer Store
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ

    C->>G: Tao ride / confirm booking
    G->>R: createRide
    R->>MQ: ride.finding_driver_requested
    MQ->>G: matching request
    G->>D: tim driver online gan nhat
    D-->>G: danh sach driver phu hop
    G-->>Driver: NEW_RIDE_AVAILABLE
    R->>X: set ride:offer:{rideId}
    R->>X: sadd ride:offered:{rideId}

    alt Driver chap nhan trong thoi gian TTL
        Driver->>G: accept-offer
        G->>R: acceptOffer
        R->>X: del ride:offer:{rideId}
        R->>MQ: ride.assigned / ride.accepted
        MQ->>G: fan-out trang thai
        G-->>C: RIDE_STATUS_UPDATE
    else Driver timeout hoac reject
        X-->>R: offer expired / cancelOffer
        R->>X: sadd ride:rejected:{rideId}
        R->>MQ: ride.offer_timeout
        alt Chua vuot so lan reassign
            R->>MQ: ride.reassignment_requested
            MQ->>G: matching request moi
        else Dat nguong toi da
            R->>MQ: ride.reassignment_failed
            G-->>C: thong bao khong tim thay tai xe
        end
    end
